name: Dear Mother Nature,
description:
Dear Mother Nature,

There's a green bee in this golden flower
(and so much more)
I see in you so much power
The balance and the beauty...
Everyday you have this duty
To keep things perfect, it must be exhausting
Humans destroying you, Mother Nature you're falling
There's no resilience that can keep up with this destruction
Selfish men, only thinking 'bout production
We won't produce anything when there's nothing left
Day by day humans keep committing theft
They steal from you, it's time for you to fight back
Cause we'll all die if all that's left is black.
